    public static final class PrimitiveSet.Entry<P>

      • getPrimitive

        public P getPrimitive()
        Returns the primitive for this entry.

        For primitives of type Mac, Aead, PublicKeySign, PublicKeyVerify, DeterministicAead, HybridEncrypt, and HybridDecrypt this is a primitive which ignores the output prefix and assumes "RAW".
